      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone looking for utility over aesthetics. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor dings, and the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and floor mats. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, though it may require some upcoming maintenance like new tires or a brake service to bring it back to peak performance. It\u2019s a solid, functional vehicle that has been well-used and is priced accordingly for its current state.",
