      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning motorist. Maintained to a high standard, it exhibits a refined aesthetic and reliable mechanical integrity. Every aspect of this automobile reflects a commitment to consistent care, offering a sophisticated driving experience and exceptional long-term value. We invite you to experience the performance and prestige of a vehicle that remains in commendable condition.",
