    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been super reliable and is in really solid shape\u2014honestly, it\u2019s a joy to drive! I\u2019ve taken good care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road for its next adventure. Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out on a road trip, this ride won't let you down. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
